# ---- .NET / Visual Studio / Rider / VSCode ----
## Build results
**/bin/
**/obj/
**/artifacts/

## User-specific files
**/*.user
**/*.suo
**/*.userosscache
**/*.sln.docstates
**/*.csproj.user

## IDE folders
.vs/
.idea/
.vscode/

## OS files
[Tt]humbs.db
[Dd]esktop.ini

## Logs
**/*.log
**/logs/

# ---- ASP.NET / local secrets ----
**/appsettings.*.local.json
**/appsettings.local.json
**/secrets.json

# ---- EF Core ----
## Keep migrations tracked (do NOT ignore Migrations folders)
## but ignore local DB files if any appear
**/*.db
**/*.db-shm
**/*.db-wal

# ---- Docker ----
**/.env
**/.env.*
docker-compose.override.yml

# ---- Test results / coverage ----
**/TestResults/
**/*.trx
**/*.coverage
**/*.coveragexml
**/coverage*/

# ---- NuGet ----
## packages folder is usually not used in SDK-style projects, but ignore if present
**/packages/
## per-user machine caches should not be committed
**/project.lock.json
**/project.fragment.lock.json

# ---- Misc ----
**/*.nupkg
**/*.snupkg
**/*.pdb
**/*.cache
**/.DS_Store

